For example , even as 3 M was producing at 100 percent of its capacity ( 35 million N-95 masks <TIMEX3 tid="t551" type="DURATION" value="P1M">a month</TIMEX3> ) , a single hospital in New York City used up more than two million masks in <TIMEX3 tid="t549" type="DATE" value="2020-02">February</TIMEX3> , before the surge in Covid-19 cases there .
