More machines might , at best , be manufactured by the hundreds <TIMEX3 tid="t555" type="DURATION" value="P1M">a month</TIMEX3> — but not by the thousands , as is needed <TIMEX3 tid="t553" type="DATE" value="PRESENT_REF">right now</TIMEX3> .
It is precisely in the face of such hard truths that a national strategy and leadership are crucial .
