“ It struck me as this is a real issue for many of us , and in our own community . ”
<TIMEX3 tid="t1351" type="DATE" value="2020-03-04">Four days later</TIMEX3> , he and his executive team told tens of thousands of Microsoft employees in the Seattle area that they could work at home .
