Apple has generally priced its iPhones high and marketed them as objects of desire , but it has taken the budget approach before .
<TIMEX3 tid="t2709" type="DATE" value="2016">Four years ago</TIMEX3> , the company released the first iPhone SE , which also featured an older design with sped - up internals , for $ 399 .
